  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Geisha Clan, Level 4+ <br />You dedicated yourself body and soul to becoming the best Geisha you can. You gain the following:</p><ul><li>You can choose an additional skill to gain mastery from the High Nobility trait that you did not choose yet to gain mastery in, you gain proficiency with that skill. If you already have proficiency, you gain one rank of mastery with it, At level 8, this skill gains one additional rank of mastery for free.</li><li><p>Depending on the specialty of Geisha you chose, you gain a +1 modifier to one of the following:</p><ul><li><strong>Dancer:</strong> +1 to Dexterity or Strength</li><li><strong>Strategic:</strong> +1 to Intelligence or Wisdom</li><li><strong>Eloquence:</strong> +1 to Wisdom or Charisma</li></ul></li></ul>",
